### C. Missing Database Migrations
The database schema is empty except for default Laravel tables. The application uses SQLite (`database/database.sqlite`), but lacks table structures for:
*   `trips` (title, location, capacity, etc.)
*   `events` (image_path, title, location, capacity, tags, etc.)
*   `favorites` (joins user and trip)
*   `itineraries` / `itinerary_items` (days, items, icons, times, etc.)

Currently, only the default migrations are present in [database/migrations/](file:///c:/Users/kj-acer/Desktop/23rd_Batch_CebuTra_Offline/database/migrations):
1.  `0001_01_01_000000_create_users_table.php`
2.  `0001_01_01_000001_create_cache_table.php`
3.  `0001_01_01_000002_create_jobs_table.php`

